stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> Init

    Init --> DegradedMode: No Trust Anchor<br>OR Cert REVOKED/EXPIRED
    Init --> TcpOnly: Cert PENDING/PENDING_APPROVAL<br>OR SCHEDULED_OFFLINE<br>(TLS never yet established)
    Init --> TcpReady: Cert VALID<br>AND Monitoring Required<br>(awaiting first GOOD)
    Init --> TlsReady: Cert VALID<br>AND Monitoring NOT Required

    TcpOnly --> TlsReady: Cert Status GOOD<br>(monitoring confirmed VALID)
    TcpOnly --> DegradedMode: Cert REVOKED or EXPIRED

    TcpReady --> TlsReady: Cert Status GOOD
    TcpReady --> DegradedMode: Cert Status BAD (REVOKED/EXPIRED)<br>OR persistent STALE

    TlsReady --> TcpOnly: Cert Status SUSPENDED<br>(SCHEDULED_OFFLINE or PENDING_RENEWAL)
    TlsReady --> TcpReady: Cert Status UNKNOWN<br>(PVACMS momentarily unreachable)
    TlsReady --> DegradedMode: Cert Status BAD (REVOKED/EXPIRED)
